Release udiskie v2.5.2

- drop external dependency on distutils (#278)
- rename ``--notify-command`` to ``--event-hook`` to prevent misunderstandings (#279)
Update language files

Rename --notify-command to --event-hook

Closes #279

Replace external dependency on distutils

Fixes #278

Release udiskie v2.5.1

- fix default install location for bash completion scripts (#275)
- fix zsh completion for device names with spaces (#253)
Merge branch 'update-release-script'
Switch back to normal release mode
Test release
Small cleanup

Use pypa/gh-actions-pypi-publish for releasing

In order to support trusted publishing.

I believe twine doesn't support it yet, see:

https://github.com/pypa/twine/issues/999

Add python 3.10 to workflow

Waiting with 3.11/3.12 for now because keyutils has no wheel for these
versions as of yet.
Merge branch 'fix-zsh-completion-for-devices-with-spaces'

Fix zsh completion for device names with spaces

Resolves #253

Rename _canonical_paths to avoid interference

Also, start using our local version.

Import _canonical_paths from zsh 5.9

As installed in:

    /usr/share/zsh/functions/Completion/Unix/_canonical_paths

Found in the source repository at:

    Completion/Unix/Type/_canonical_paths

Fix folder for bash completions

Thanks for the report to @patlefort!

Resolves #275
